33:11.923 --> 33:15.360 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
STUART ROTHENBERG: I think we
will see more of this don't give
Hillary Clinton a blank

33:15.360 --> 33:19.064 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
