House and the Senate in states
that are competitive.

33:19.064 --> 33:21.867 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think Republicans actually
do have a fighting chance to
hold on onto the Senate.

33:21.867 --> 33:23.702 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I didn't think so six
months ago, but I do now.

33:23.702 --> 33:26.137 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
