husband, and we see something,
maybe we will stop.

35:38.937 --> 35:41.806 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: My name
is Corey Gil-Shuster.

35:41.806 --> 35:45.443 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I run The Ask an Israeli,
Ask a Palestinian Project.

35:45.443 --> 35:48.013 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you were driving on the
highway and you saw an Israeli
on the side of the road that

35:48.013 --> 35:49.247 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
