36:07.365 --> 36:10.335 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
People from all around the world
send me questions through
e-mail.

36:10.335 --> 36:15.006 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I choose the questions, and then
I go out to the streets of
Israel and Palestine to

36:15.006 --> 36:17.776 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
