Palestinians to answer the
questions themselves.

36:17.776 --> 36:21.946 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
I don't edit any
content out of it.

36:21.946 --> 36:29.821 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DURA, Palestinian: Most, the
majority, they want two states,
