They are very primitive.

36:33.858 --> 36:37.228 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And they cannot build a
country like we did.

36:37.228 --> 36:42.867 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator): For
sure, the Israelis will be
destroyed because Palestine

36:42.867 --> 36:45.537 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
