36:45.537 --> 36:49.207 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER:
Destroyed as in killed?

36:49.207 --> 36:53.912 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
WOMAN (through translator):
They should be killed, yes.

36:53.912 --> 36:56.648 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: What are you
willing to compromise for peace?

36:56.648 --> 36:57.749 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DROR, Israeli: Everything.

36:57.749 --> 37:00.185 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
My pants.

37:00.185 --> 37:03.354 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: The question
