37:11.429 --> 37:13.031 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: OK, why?

37:13.031 --> 37:15.133 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
NOGA TARNOPOLSKY: Because
it's a leading question.

37:15.133 --> 37:18.103 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: A lot of the
questions I get are what I call
gotcha questions.

37:18.103 --> 37:21.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They're a little bit over the
top, or exaggerated, or have a
very overly simplistic way of
looking

37:21.339 --> 37:24.175 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
