Palestinians to hear what people
from outside think.

37:35.520 --> 37:38.256 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And I want them to
answer in an honest way.

37:38.256 --> 37:39.924 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NOGA TARNOPOLSKY: The answer is
sometimes I do and sometimes I
don't.

37:39.924 --> 37:41.126 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: OK, what way
-- OK, so, give me an example.

37:41.126 --> 37:46.898 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Why do you think yes and
why do you think no?

37:46.898 --> 37:51.636 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NOGA TARNOPOLSKY: I think the
investment that Israel is making
