38:23.301 --> 38:30.842 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
We are on our way now to
Qalandiya checkpoint into the
West Bank.

38:30.842 --> 38:39.350 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And from there, we are going
to head out to Nablus.

38:39.350 --> 38:41.286 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
This is the Qalandiya
checkpoint.

38:41.286 --> 38:46.491 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
It's a major checkpoint,
actually much more for
Palestinians coming into Israel
who have

38:46.491 --> 38:51.062 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
permits or Jerusalem --
Palestinian Jerusalemites who
work in the West Bank, so they
go back

38:51.062 --> 38:53.531 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and forth.

38:53.531 --> 38:56.167 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Nablus is actually my favorite
-- I think this is my favorite
city in the West Bank.

38:56.167 --> 38:58.803 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
It kind of has everything.

38:58.803 --> 39:02.207 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
