lively all the time.

39:14.986 --> 39:20.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The law is that Jewish Israelis
are not allowed legally to be in
certain areas of the West

39:20.491 --> 39:22.260 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Bank.

39:22.260 --> 39:24.996 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
