going to be killed.

39:27.765 --> 39:28.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MANAR: My name is Manar.

39:28.733 --> 39:30.235 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I'm a translator.

39:30.235 --> 39:36.040 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
I'm 30 years old, and
I'm from Ramallah.

39:36.040 --> 39:40.178 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Some people find it, I won't say
offensive, but they don't like
that he lives in Tel Aviv.

39:40.178 --> 39:44.215 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
We don't say that he is Israeli.

39:44.215 --> 39:48.353 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And it's better, because people
would be more comfortable that
way.

39:48.353 --> 39:57.395 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: Do you think
this project will have much of
an impact?

39:57.395 --> 40:00.298 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MANAR: I hope so.

40:00.298 --> 40:04.569 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I really hope so, because it's
about bringing people closer
together.

40:04.569 --> 40:09.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
COREY GIL-SHUSTER: I do this
because I think it's so
important that, if you want to
solve

40:09.040 --> 40:11.843 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
