target market is.

44:53.658 --> 44:56.260 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And it's a niche.

44:56.260 --> 44:59.063 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's not broad, like Target or
Wal-Mart, but they have a
specific segment.

44:59.063 --> 45:00.998 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
They can address that segment.

45:00.998 --> 45:03.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: That
segment is very high-end.

45:03.100 --> 45:06.437 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
A simple T-shirt costs $80.

45:06.437 --> 45:10.241 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Lightweight jackets start in the
mid-$200s and go up from there.

45:10.241 --> 45:13.678 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
English admits he's serving
a specific market.

45:13.678 --> 45:19.750 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
DAN ENGLISH: We have a saying
here, that our goal is to make
competition irrelevant.

45:19.750 --> 45:22.887 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And if we try to do the same
thing that other big brands are
doing, you know, it just won't

45:22.887 --> 45:25.556 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
work.

45:25.556 --> 45:28.426 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Voormi
clothing has been getting
positive reviews in sports
magazines.

45:28.426 --> 45:32.196 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But whether the company will be
able to meet increasing demand
while keeping its commitment

45:32.196 --> 45:35.399 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to rural economic development
remains to be seen.

