46:17.541 --> 46:19.944 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And welcome to you.

46:19.944 --> 46:19.977 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MYCHAL DENZEL SMITH, Author,
"Invisible Man, Got the Whole
World Watching: A Young Black

46:19.977 --> 46:21.712 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
Man's Education": Thank
you for having me.

46:21.712 --> 46:22.647 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Let's start with
that question, how did you learn
to be a black man?

46:22.647 --> 46:24.148 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
