46:27.284 --> 46:31.155 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MYCHAL DENZEL SMITH: Well, so
the book has its Genesis after
George Zimmerman killed

46:31.155 --> 46:35.092 align:left position:25%,start line:86.67% size:75%
