right, the nuances of our
experience.

47:33.284 --> 47:36.854 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Walking through racism is
important, but how are we
dealing with talking about
patriarchy

47:36.854 --> 47:41.325 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
