class race elitism and mental
illness?

47:41.325 --> 47:44.361 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We're not including these things
in the narrative around young
black men.

47:44.361 --> 47:47.932 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Well, you do that
